description:
Video editing : Dana Khiangte
Recording : AWR Studio
Music performed and mixed by C Lalhmuaka.

Lyrics
An sawi Kanan ram nuam lam panin ka kak mek a
Kawng lakah chimbuai tu an tam thin ngei e
Mahse khawvel ropui na leh hausak an te 
An chuai leh mai thin Isu nang tel lo chuan
Ka kawng zawhah thlipui ruahpui an hrang vel thin a
Lungpui lian tak ten ka kawng zawh an dal thin
Mahse hei hian beisei na eng min siamsak thin
Ka hma lawkah ka in a awm tawh tih hi
Chorus:
Ka vanin nuam ka thlen ve hun chuan
Ka mit ngeiin ka hmu ve tawh ang I hmel duhawm chu
Chutah nang I awm dawn a ni tih ka hriatna hian
Ka khualzin kawng bumboh te a tinuam thin

Nang ka rin avangin he ka khualzin kawngah hian
Khawvel miten min tuithlar thin mah sela
Min bansan tir thei chuang lo'ng ka rinna che hi
Ka Lal leh thiantha ber chu I ni si
Vawi tam mittui tla in ka zinkawng zawh mah ila
Ka in ngei ka lo thlen ve hunah chuan in
Ka pelh hnu ka khualzin kawng chanchin te hrilin 
I kiangah ka leng ve tawh ang chatuan in.
